Bic:

Computer: Rodimus is out of the base and within defendable perimeter.

Blackfang looked at Katya as if he was saying "see, I told you".

Katya: All right, I admit your technology is advanced. Happy now?

Blackfang: Well I will brag about this moral victory, y'know...

Katya: Let us go meet Rodimus will ya?

They both went outside and saw the maximal leader in the rubbles.

Katya: Rodimus! We have to talk.
